parsed.iteration_assessment: The first iteration focused on architecture, scoring modest improvements in correctness and value through code style guidelines. Weaknesses include missing red-team testing results and live environment ESLint test coverage.

next_iteration_seeds.title: Red Team Simulation
next_iteration_seeds.rationale: Given weaknesses in red-team testing and consistency issues, an attack simulation should improve robustness.

next_iteration_seeds.title: Live Environment Testing with ESLint
next_iteration_seeds.rationale: Extending tests to the actual working environment will ensure reliability meets real-world conditions and can help identify inconsistencies or errors missed in testing.
